### AI Recommendation API Tests

# 1. Check service status
GET http://localhost:4000/api/ai-recommendations/status
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

###

# 2. Get recommendations for a project (replace PROJECT_ID)
GET http://localhost:4000/api/ai-recommendations/projects/PROJECT_ID/annotators?maxRecommendations=10
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

###

# 3. Send bulk invitations (replace PROJECT_ID and ANNOTATOR_IDS)
POST http://localhost:4000/api/ai-recommendations/projects/PROJECT_ID/send-invitations
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "annotatorIds": ["ANNOTATOR_ID_1", "ANNOTATOR_ID_2"],
  "customMessage": "We're excited to invite you to this special project!"
}